OL,3,CLabour revolt grows ahead of key
OL,4,Cwelfare vote, with at least 54 MPs set
OL,5,Cto rebel
OL,7,FBy Senior Politics Producers Maya
OL,8,FBowles and Lili Donlon-Mansbridge
OL,10,FAt least 54 Labour MPs are set to
OL,11,Frebel against government plans to
OL,12,Fradically change the welfare system,
OL,13,Fpaving the way for the prime
OL,14,Fminister's biggest revolt yet.
OL,16,FITV News has been tracking how Labour
OL,17,FMPs plan to vote, and understands 54
OL,18,Fwill go against the government's plans
OL,19,Fto slash benefits for millions of
OL,20,Fpeople.
