OL,7,FAs rebelling MPs scramble to gather
OL,8,Fsupport and Downing Street strive to
OL,9,Fmake sure the plans are voted through,
OL,10,Feveryone is trying to put a number on
OL,11,Fexactly how many MPs could vote
OL,12,Fagainst the government.
OL,14,FITV News has that number at 54 -
OL,15,Fincluding 42 who publicly signed a
OL,16,Fletter against the cuts, and an
OL,17,Fadditional 12 who have privately said
OL,18,Fthey can't back the plans.
