OL,7,FWhile 42 MPs have come out publicly,
OL,8,Fmore than 100 MPs are understood to
OL,9,Fhave signed a private letter urging
OL,10,Fthe government to delay the changes
OL,11,Fand rethink. ITV News understands
OL,12,Fthere are at least six MPs who have
OL,13,Fsigned both letters.
OL,15,FBut many Labour backbenchers believe a
OL,16,Flarge chunk of the MPs who have signed
OL,17,Fthe private letter won't actually vote
OL,18,Fagainst the plans, and are instead
OL,19,Flikely to abstain or ultimately vote
OL,20,Fwith the government.
