OL,4,Cwelfare vote, with at least 54 MPs set
OL,5,Cto rebel
OL,7,FDespite that, one senior Number 10
OL,8,Ffigure told ITV News' Deputy Political
OL,9,FEditor Anushka Asthana they feared up
OL,10,Fto 100 MPs could oppose the plans, and
OL,11,Fif the vote had happened last week in
OL,12,Fthe wake of the local elections, it
OL,13,Fwould likely inflict a bloody nose on
OL,14,FStarmer's administration.
OL,16,FMany Labour MPs have told ITV News
OL,17,Fthey're still deciding how to vote,
OL,18,Fand waiting to see the actual detail
OL,19,Fof the legislation they'll be voting
OL,20,Fon.
