OL,3,CLabour revolt grows ahead of key
OL,4,Cwelfare vote, with at least 54 MPs set
OL,5,Cto rebel
OL,7,FThere's no doubt the welfare vote is
OL,8,Flikely to see the biggest rebellion of
OL,9,FStarmer's premiership, and if all
OL,10,Fopposition parties vote against the
OL,11,Fplans, only 83 Labour MPs need to vote
OL,12,Fagainst the government to defeat the
OL,13,Flegislation.
OL,15,FIn a vote expected to take place in
OL,16,FJune, MPs will decide whether to pass
OL,17,Fthe Starmer's plans to shake up the
OL,18,Fwelfare system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
