OL,3,CLabour revolt grows ahead of key
OL,4,Cwelfare vote, with at least 54 MPs set
OL,5,Cto rebel
OL,7,FThe government plan to make it harder
OL,8,Ffor disabled people to claim Personal
OL,9,FIndependence Payments (Pip), and to
OL,10,Ffreeze universal credit incapacity
OL,11,Fbenefits for existing claimants, while
OL,12,Fcutting them by 50% for new claimants.
OL,14,FThe plans are expected to save #5bn
OL,15,Ffrom the ballooning welfare budget,
OL,16,Fbut critics warn the move will push
OL,17,Fvulnerable people into poverty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
