OL,7,FThe Guardian newspaper also obtained
OL,8,Fgovernment forecasts last week that
OL,9,Fshowed the cuts will hit 700,000
OL,10,Ffamilies who are already in poverty,
OL,11,Fon top of the projected 250,000.
OL,13,FMany of the MPs who have come out in
OL,14,Fopposition to the plans are calling
OL,15,Ffor them to be delayed until the full
OL,16,Fassessment of cuts can be laid out,
OL,17,Fand for the consultation on the
OL,18,Fwelfare reform to be expanded to allow
OL,19,Fdisabled people and key stakeholders
OL,20,Fto engage in more detail.
