OL,7,FOne Labour MP told ITV News: "I didn't
OL,8,Fbecome a Labour MP to make people
OL,9,Fpoorer", and was particularly critical
OL,10,Fof the Pip cuts, saying the government
OL,11,Fwere trying to sell a "cuts agenda as
OL,12,Freform".
OL,14,FWhen pressed on whether she might
OL,15,Fchange course in light of the growing
OL,16,Frebellion, Work and Pensions Secretary
OL,17,FLiz Kendall stood by the radical
OL,18,Fchanges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
