OL,7,FIn an interview with ITV News Digital
OL,8,FPolitical Reporter Lewis Denison,
OL,9,FDisability Minister Stephen Timms
OL,10,Ffailed to rule out coming back for
OL,11,Ffurther welfare cuts in the Autumn.
OL,13,F"There's lots of discussions going on
OL,14,Fat the moment, I'm very focused on the
OL,15,Fpackage we set out in March", he said.
OL,17,FHis boss Liz Kendall pushed back at
OL,18,Freports of further cuts, saying "we
OL,19,Fdon't have any plans for that".
